      Library Gallery Items    </h2>
    
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="view view-item-gallery view-id-item_gallery view-display-id-default view-dom-id-4c9445c032eb75a5bd6f1afcc49dfd1c">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
      <div class="holder">    <ul>          <li class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Billy Lynn&#039;s Long Halftime Walk</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/billy.jpg?itok=i7Elq37Y" width="83" height="120" alt="Billy Lynn&#039;s Long Halftime Walk" title="Billy Lynn&#039;s Long Halftime Walk" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>A razor-sharp satire set in Texas during America's war in Iraq. It explores the gaping national disconnect between the war at home and the war abroad.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">The Lion&#039;s Mouth</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/lions%20mouth.jpg?itok=xq8j-EGX" width="83" height="125" alt="The Lion&#039;s Mouth" title="The Lion&#039;s Mouth" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Filled with lies, deception, and the truth about government, The Lion’s Mouth questions who truly holds the power in Norway, and how far they will go to keep it. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-3 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Opposite of Everyone: a Novel</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/opposite.jpg?itok=77NTyQRq" width="83" height="126" alt="Opposite of Everyone: a Novel" title="Opposite of Everyone: a Novel" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>A story about story itself, how the tales we tell connect us, break us, and define us, and how the endings and beginnings we choose can destroy us . . . and make us whole.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-4 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Shoot: A Valentino Mystery</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/shoot.jpg?itok=cO9_dv58" width="83" height="124" alt="Shoot: A Valentino Mystery" title="Shoot: A Valentino Mystery" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>In the surreal world of Hollywood, what is on screen is rarely reality. As he races to uncover the truth before time runs out, his heroes begin their fall from grace. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-5 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Girl With All the Gifts</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/girl.jpg?itok=yIEEXYE1" width="81" height="127" alt="Girl With All the Gifts" title="Girl With All the Gifts" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Every morning, Melanie waits in her cell to be collected for class. When they come for her, Sergeant Parks keeps his gun pointing at her while two of his people strap her into the wheelchair. She thinks they don't like her. She jokes...</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-6 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Amazing Adventures of Kavalier Clay</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/amazing.jpg?itok=LrUFE-hR" width="80" height="127" alt="Amazing Adventures of Kavalier Clay" title="Amazing Adventures of Kavalier Clay" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Joe Kavalier, a young Jewish artist who has also been trained in the art of Houdini-esque escape, has just smuggled himself out of Nazi-invaded Prague and landed in New York City. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-7 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">A Book of Common Prayer</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/book.jpg?itok=QkxANzJq" width="79" height="127" alt="A Book of Common Prayer" title="A Book of Common Prayer" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>The story of two American women in the derelict Central American nation of Boca Grande. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-8 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Fancy Nancy: Saturday Night Sleepover</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/fancy.jpg?itok=6W1PbsJW" width="83" height="83" alt="Fancy Nancy: Saturday Night Sleepover" title="Fancy Nancy: Saturday Night Sleepover" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>When Nancy's parents win an all-expenses-paid vacation, Nancy and JoJo get to sleep over at their neighbor's home, Mrs. DeVine's. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-9 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">That&#039;s Not Bunny!</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/bunny.jpg?itok=3FqKALdT" width="83" height="92" alt="That&#039;s Not Bunny!" title="That&#039;s Not Bunny!" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>From high above on his perch, Hawk searches for his next meal. When he spots a bunny he swoops down and snatches-a carrot!? </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-10 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Famous Phonies</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/famous.jpg?itok=WH8alu_O" width="83" height="117" alt="Famous Phonies" title="Famous Phonies" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Explore the underbelly of history and question everything you thought you knew about history’s finest. Follow the fake lives of these twelve history-changers to uncover the fabrications of the famous, and the should-be-famous!</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-11 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Pax</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/pax.png?itok=5fYaIErB" width="83" height="118" alt="Pax" title="Pax" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>A beautifully wrought, utterly compelling novel about the powerful relationship between a boy and his fox. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-12 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Lego: Jurassic World (PS4 Game)</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/lego%20ps4.jpg?itok=0kUoGNSe" width="83" height="93" alt="Lego: Jurassic World (PS4 Game)" title="Lego: Jurassic World (PS4 Game)" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Relive key moments from all four Jurassic films and wreak havoc as LEGO dinosaurs!</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-13 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Shhh! This Book is Sleeping</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/shh.jpg?itok=OlZ_FpsV" width="83" height="113" alt="Shhh! This Book is Sleeping" title="Shhh! This Book is Sleeping" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>A mouse inside the pages invites you to read the book a bedtime story, tuck it in with a cozy blanket, and give it a hug and a kiss. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-14 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Farm</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/farm.jpg?itok=Igxpo1K-" width="83" height="103" alt="Farm" title="Farm" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Children will read about what it is like to live and work on a farm, and they will see beautiful photographs depicting everyday life with the farm animals. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-15 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Blaze and the Monster Machines: Racing Colors!</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/racing.jpg?itok=lSnV2Exi" width="83" height="114" alt="Blaze and the Monster Machines: Racing Colors!" title="Blaze and the Monster Machines: Racing Colors!" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>The awesome trucks from Nickelodeon's Blaze and the Monster Machines introduce basic colors in this sturdy board book that's perfect for boys ages 0 to 3.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-16 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Nest</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/nest.jpg?itok=Aj-QuK_w" width="83" height="87" alt="Nest" title="Nest" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Artist Jorey Hurley pairs vivid, crisp artwork with simple, minimal text—often just one word per spread—to create a breathtaking, peaceful chronicle of nature and life’s milestones.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-17 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Paw Patrol: Team Numbers</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/paw.jpg?itok=MiZ38iew" width="83" height="114" alt="Paw Patrol: Team Numbers" title="Paw Patrol: Team Numbers" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>The playful puppies from Nickelodeon's PAW Patrol introduce numbers in this sturdy board book that's perfect for boys and girls ages 0 to 3.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-18 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Meditation for Beginners (DVD)</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/meditation.jpg?itok=WWrugnBG" width="83" height="114" alt="Meditation for Beginners (DVD)" title="Meditation for Beginners (DVD)" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Ease tension and anxiety through the simple art of meditation. Yoga and meditation instructor Maritza guides you step-by-step in the practice of mindfulness so you can calm and center yourself.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-19 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Six Week Six Pack - Jillian Michaels (DVD)</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/jillian.jpg?itok=BtOEfkwj" width="83" height="117" alt="Six Week Six Pack - Jillian Michaels (DVD)" title="Six Week Six Pack - Jillian Michaels (DVD)" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Forget boring sit-ups – Jillian’s ab-shredding system will chisel the midsection with her winning combination of core-focused cardio circuits and ab-toning exercises. </p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-20 views-row-even">  
          <h3 class="field-content">The Bet</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/the%20bet.jpg?itok=ekPsjqnX" width="83" height="126" alt="The Bet" title="The Bet" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>The minute Jake mentions his ill grandmother, Kacey is ready to do anything for the sweet old woman. And if that means pretending they're engaged for her sake-so be it.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-21 views-row-odd">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Newcomer&#039;s Guide to Canada</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/newcomer.jpg?itok=eapiixd0" width="83" height="124" alt="Newcomer&#039;s Guide to Canada" title="Newcomer&#039;s Guide to Canada" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Highlights the most important information newcomers need to know before they arrive in Canada and what they need to know once they arrive.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
          <li class="views-row views-row-22 views-row-even views-row-last">  
          <h3 class="field-content">Into the Fury</h3>    
          <img src="http://www.thoroldpubliclibrary.ca/sites/default/files/styles/large/public/into.jpg?itok=ZNtKrKti" width="78" height="127" alt="Into the Fury" title="Into the Fury" />    
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content"><p>Ethan's learned the hard way that beauty is no substitute for character. So even though Valentine Hart is one of the most breathtaking women he's ever seen, he's keeping his hands off and his eyes open.</p>
</div>  </div></li>
      </ul></div>    </div>
  
  
  
  
